text: Jim Houlihan (1898–1967) was an Irish sportsperson. He played hurling with his local club Tulla and was a member of the Clare senior inter-county team in the 1920s and 1930s. ==References== Category:1898 births Category:1967 deaths Category:Tulla hurlers (Clare) Category:Clare inter-county hurlers Category:Munster inter-provincial hurlers
